  "chapter_summary": "第二十三回　金府双卫。剑客行故事继续。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凌风公子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "水……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南第一美人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南第一美人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展小侠！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想你是渴坏了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小红",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "红姐姐，不要看不起人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哎呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的消息，可倒灵通！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁背驼龙",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展兄，已清醒了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展兄误浴'寒泉水'，寒闭百窍，又被三杯热酒一逼，是以昏绝过去，但不要紧，虽然周身筋络尽散，暂时不能行动，好在我家还有解寒驱毒之药，不出三日，展兄便可好了，这……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倒是巧得很啊！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哈哈！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁翼飞鹏",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁翼驼龙",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金府双铁卫",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小红",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展兄好好养息吧，三日保证你痊愈！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金府双铁卫",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请道其详。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我说你不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你父亲！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我父亲就住在家中。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他住在什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青蚨神金九，江湖上有几人不知令尊的大名。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只闻名未见面？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "祥麟公子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么病一好，就急着要走呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想是我家不好或……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我倒没有那么说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道多住一夜也不行吗？……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南第一美人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 236,
