      "listener": null,
      "text": "无情碧剑",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青蚨神",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玉面小青蚨",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁要你来多管闲事！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玉面小青蚨",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师哥不在家，我不管你谁来管你，难道让你把金家的脸都给丢光吗……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拍！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我有什么丢脸？哥哥也不敢这样骂我……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样说来，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玉面小青蚨",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我金彩凤不是自夸，见到我的人，没有一个不说我生得美，百般向我献殷勤，想接近我的青年男子，更不知有多少，但我从没有爱过任何人，自从见了展小侠，不知怎么，我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孟如萍！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玉面小青蚨",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神龙出水",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 330,
